3D Mammography Bus Event
Join us quarterly in 2025 from 10 AM to 3 PM at Tradition Square for a mobile mammography event. Take advantage of this convenient opportunity to get your mammogram and receive same-day results read by Dr. Ryan Polselli, a fellowship-trained breast imaging radiologist. All insurance plans are accepted, appointments take only ten minutes, and there is no prescription required.
For the upcoming screening event on September 9th, 3D Mobile Mammography is offering a special incentive: a $20 Amazon E-Gift Card for every woman who completes her mammogram. Our goal is to encourage more women to schedule and attend their appointments.
To receive the gift card, participants must provide a valid email address at the time of their appointment. E-Gift Cards will be emailed after the mammogram has been completed.
Schedule your appointment today by clicking
HERE
.
Or by phone: 844-546-5871
